Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.59,0:00:03.44,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,O próximo é um novato que vai\N participar pela primeira vez.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:06.55,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,O carro 86 é de um piloto da Inglaterra.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:09.07,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata Katagiri, 19 anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:11.07,Italics,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.08,Italics,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Não brinca? É ele mesmo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:25.09,Italics,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Por que você está aqui, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:30.42,Italics,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Sou eu ou ela pareceu surpresa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:30.42,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Six. Five. Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:32.91,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Three. Two. One.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:38.42,Italics,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata...
